name: Pennington Barrel Mover with 2 in. Wheels
description: The 13 in. Barrel Mover helps to transport bigger pots to any location. They are also great for moving sporting equipment, garden equipment, heavy pails, and more. The barrel mover features a weather-resistant stain for durability.
